#1. Create a greeting for your program.

#2. Ask the user for the city that they grew up in.

#3. Ask the user for the name of a pet.

#4. Combine the name of their city and pet and show them their band name.

#5. Make sure the input cursor shows on a new line, see the example at:
#   https://band-name-generator-end.appbrewery.repl.run/

print("Hello Welcome to programe generator")
yourCity=input("Which city you grew up in:?\n")   #take note of \n to place the cursor on the next line
pet=input("What is the name of yor pet?\n")
print("your band name is "+yourCity+" "+pet)

